Package diacheck.java.libs.imageTools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControlFieldReader
    ControlFieldReader is created solely for the purpose of finding control fields in a sample image and read the position and orientation of those fields.
    Field
    Represents a field from the sample image, containing pixel data for entire field.
    FieldFinder
    Fieldfinder is a class for locating specific data fields within an image.
    ImageReader  
    ImageTransformer
    ImageTransformer is mainly the class responsible for manipulating the data in the image file.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FieldType
    Each FieldType describes the permitted color input for each type of field found in a sample image.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HighNoiseException
    This exception indicates that the source image contains too much noise and therefore renders the image unusable for color analysis.
    IllegalInputDataException
